reviewText: Best option since they do not have conferences near my home to go to.

Have never been to a "Women of Faith" conference so this is the next best thing. Patsy Clairmont and Sheila Walsh are enjoyable speakers and I feel inspired by their overcoming the deep hurts of their past. I also enjoyed listening to all of the women speakers. I was also impressed with the women who led the music worship segments.  The hope and faith they share truly is contagious.

I just love these conferences. I used to go to a church that had a group that went every year. Since moving I no longer have a group to go with, so have missed quite a few, and this is a great way to listen and be encouraged. The speakers are so relatable and I love that I can pull the DVD's out periodically and listen again. Great product, great price.
came in great shape and played wonderfully

This DVD would not play on my DVD player.  I took it to work and tried to play it on my computer and it would not play.  I tried it on my computer at home - it would not play.  I tried it on a friends' DVD player - it would not play.  It would just sit and spin and never actually engage in the DVD player.  This is the second DVD of this conference thatI have purchased (from two different sellers) that did not play..

There were problems with the DVDs initially but the seller was able to correct the problem (very graciously).  Since it has been several months since I made the purchase I cannot recall exactly what the problem was, but everything was rectified quickly and to my satifaction.  I had attended the Women of Faith Conference, Contagious Joy, in 2006 so I knew the content of the DVDs would be great.
These videos are exactly what I expected and MORE... I love them!! I watched the whole thing the first day I got it!! I love it!
